This is an excel report built with excel power query together with pivot table. 

It is designed to reflect the weekly advertising situtation for real estates in different districts through measurement 
like total number of advertisements, hit rate of advertisement. Data in workbooks could be updated easily by a simple refresh.

This excel demonstrates:
1. how data should be imported and formulated by power query from databases, 
2. how pivot table should be set up to compare performance metrics weekly 
3. how slicer could be adopted in pivot table to provide interactive experience to user
